OL,3,CJustice minister U-turn on Creeslough
OL,4,Cfamily meeting
OL,6,FThe Irish Justice Minister has now
OL,7,Fsaid he will meet with those families
OL,8,Fseeking justice over the devastating
OL,9,FCreeslough petrol station explosion.
OL,11,FOriginally, Jim O'Callaghan had
OL,12,Frejected their request for the meeting.
OL,14,FJust over a month ago UTV first
OL,15,Frevealed Mr O'Callaghan had rejected
OL,16,Ftheir requests saying he wanted to
OL,17,F"allow criminal proceedings to be
OL,18,Fcompleted".
OL,20,FFamilies described that as a "slap in
OL,21,Fthe face" at the time.
OL,26,@|D@^OU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
