FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775153467
OL,3,CJustice minister U-turn on Creeslough
OL,4,Cfamily meeting
OL,6,FThe row further intensified when
OL,7,FMinister O'Callaghan was asked about
OL,8,Fthe matter by UTV at a press
OL,9,Fconference. He said it was "not his
OL,10,Fjob to be sensitive" to the families
OL,11,Fbut rather to see justice done.
OL,13,FThe mother of a teenage girl killed in
OL,14,Fthe blast said she was relieved with
OL,15,Fthe minister's u-turn.
OL,17,FTen people were killed in a suspected
OL,18,Fgas leak at a filling station in the
OL,19,FDonegal village in 2022.
OL,20,FInvestigations into the explosion
OL,21,Fremain ongoing.
OL,26,@qD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775153467
OL,3,CJustice minister U-turn on Creeslough
OL,4,Cfamily meeting
OL,6,FDonna Harper, who lost her 14-year-old
OL,7,Fdaughter Leona, says she is
OL,8,F"delighted" Minister O'Callagan has
OL,9,Fagreed to talk to the families.
OL,11,FThey want him to call an independent
OL,12,Fpublic inquiry into the tragedy.
OL,14,FIn a statement to UTV the Republic's
OL,15,FDepartment of Justice said Minister
OL,16,FO'Callaghan will not consider a public
OL,17,Finquiry until the criminal
OL,18,Finvestigation and inquest are
OL,19,Fcompleted.
OL,26,@pD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
