PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775153467
OL,3,CJustice minister U-turn on Creeslough
OL,4,Cfamily meeting
OL,6,FA spokesperson said he will listen to
OL,7,Fthe concerns of the families. While a
OL,8,Fdate is yet to be confirmed it is
OL,9,Funderstood it will take place soon and
OL,10,Fin Dublin.
OL,12,FIt will happen against the backdrop of
OL,13,Fanother planning row.
OL,15,FLast year a planning application to
OL,16,Fredevelop the site of the explosion in
OL,17,FCreeslough was unsuccessful.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
