OL,3,CJustice minister U-turn on Creeslough
OL,4,Cfamily meeting
OL,6,FNow families are preparing to appeal
OL,7,Fafter Donegal County Council granted
OL,8,Fpermission for the construction of a
OL,9,Fnew filling station on a neighbouring
OL,10,Fsite.
OL,12,FRelatives of the victims also face an
OL,13,Fanxious wait to hear when gardai will
OL,14,Fcomplete their investigations.
OL,16,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,17,FITVX
OL,19,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,20,Fhere.
